org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network

Class WifiDirectInviteDialogMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • BroadcastReceiver
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.network.WifiDirectInviteDialogMonitor

  • public class WifiDirectInviteDialogMonitor
extends BroadcastReceiver
    WifiDirectInviteDialogMonitor monitors and controls the invite dialogs for WifiDirect connection invitations. The implementation relies on enhancements we've made to Android in our FTCAndroid build.
